---
// Benefits section component
---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-black to-gray-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6 border border-gray-700">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
        Beneficios Comprobados
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Resultados Que Hablan
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-600">
          Por Sí Solos
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Nuestras soluciones de automatización han ayudado a cientos de empresas a transformar sus operaciones 
        y alcanzar niveles de eficiencia que nunca creyeron posibles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-20">
      <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">87%</div>
        <div class="text-gray-300 font-medium">Aumento en Productividad</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-green-500/30">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">65%</div>
        <div class="text-gray-300 font-medium">Reducción de Costos</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-cyan-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/30">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">40h</div>
        <div class="text-gray-300 font-medium">Ahorradas por Semana</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/30">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">98%</div>
        <div class="text-gray-300 font-medium">Precisión en Procesos</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits Grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Benefits List -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">
              Eficiencia Máxima 24/7
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Nuestros sistemas trabajan sin descanso, procesando tareas repetitivas mientras tú te enfocas en actividades estratégicas que realmente agregan valor a tu negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-green-500/30">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">
              Eliminación de Errores Humanos
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Reduce drásticamente los errores costosos mediante procesos automatizados que garantizan consistencia y precisión en cada operación de tu empresa.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/30">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">
              ROI Comprobado en 3-6 Meses
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Recupera tu inversión rápidamente con ahorros inmediatos en costos operativos, tiempo de personal y recursos tecnológicos optimizados.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/30">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">
              Escalabilidad Inteligente
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Crece sin límites con sistemas que se adaptan automáticamente al volumen de tu negocio, manteniendo la eficiencia sin importar el tamaño.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual Element -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">
              Antes vs Después
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Transformación real de procesos</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Before -->
            <div class="bg-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-red-400/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 shadow-lg shadow-red-500/50">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h5 class="font-semibold text-red-200">Antes de EM STUDIOS</h5>
              </div>
              <ul class="text-sm text-red-100 space-y-1">
                <li>• Procesos manuales lentos</li>
                <li>• Errores frecuentes y costosos</li>
                <li>• Empleados sobrecargados</li>
                <li>• Falta de visibilidad en tiempo real</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- After -->
            <div class="bg-green-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-green-400/30 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 shadow-lg shadow-green-500/50">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h5 class="font-semibold text-green-200">Después de EM STUDIOS</h5>
              </div>
              <ul class="text-sm text-green-100 space-y-1">
                <li>• Automatización completa</li>
                <li>• Precisión del 98%+</li>
                <li>• Equipo enfocado en estrategia</li>
                <li>• Dashboards en tiempo real</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ROI Calculator -->
          <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 text-center border border-blue-400/30">
            <h5 class="font-heading font-bold text-blue-200 mb-2">Calculadora ROI</h5>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-300 mb-1 drop-shadow-lg">$18,000,000</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">Ahorro promedio anual</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-blue-300 mt-2">*Basado en empresa de 25 empleados</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating elements -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500/30 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border border-blue-400/40 animate-bounce-subtle">
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg drop-shadow-lg">87%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-green-500/30 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border border-green-400/40 animate-bounce-subtle" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg drop-shadow-lg">$45M</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 